[Hyper Street Fighter II-The Anniversary Edition Codes\Hit Anywhere (Both Players)]
author=Code Master
description=Don't use Ryu's Fierce Hurricane kick or other attacks that do a lot of damage. If your opponent is dead and you are still doing a lot of damage, it will loop infinitely playing music. Hold Select, Then Press Start To Go Back To The Main Menu.
